_sText:
This map was originally made by Moo,
and is released here with his permission.
It' s a nice remake of the oldschool
zm map zm_crazycity_b2.
We added some new rooms to fill in some
of the old buildings, which used to have
nothing inside.  We also added an
underground area and put clips on high,
unreachable areas to prevent players
from getting to them with propmenu.
Also, the map has been optimized and has
very high FPS.  It has 66 spawnpoints,
so it's good for 50+ player Servers.
